Class RMTopNSort

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.reportmill.base.RMSort
      • com.reportmill.base.RMTopNSort
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Comparator

    public class RMTopNSort
extends RMSort
    This is a sort subclass to support sorting objects by their relative position in an array of values.
